<text top="1082" left="822" width="6" height="14" font="9"><b>3</b></text>
<text top="88" left="773" width="56" height="14" font="9"><b>S/PV.4985</b></text>
<text top="132" left="126" width="324" height="17" font="2">This statement will be issued as a document of</text>
<text top="150" left="90" width="360" height="17" font="2">the Security Council under the symbol</text>
<text top="168" left="90" width="113" height="17" font="2">S/PRST/2004/19.</text>
<text top="132" left="504" width="324" height="17" font="2">The Security Council has thus concluded the</text>
<text top="150" left="468" width="360" height="17" font="2">present stage of its consideration of the item on its</text>
<text top="168" left="468" width="49" height="17" font="2">agenda.</text>
<text top="195" left="504" width="191" height="17" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 7.50 p.m.</i></text>
</page>
